flowRoot.flowPara: I am an engineer by education, a manager by profession and an interaction designer by choice, with thirteen years of experience in the software industry. After six years of working in software development, I switched to design and joined D. E. Shaw as a senior designer on their Design and User Experience team,where I have graduated to leading the entire function in Hyderabad. As a manager, engineer andinteraction designer, I find myself uniquely positioned to lead projects with a strong focus on the clientand their requirements.
